# Category demo data

`src/data/category-demo-products.ts` is **category-browsing demo data only** —
rendered as non-interactive discovery tiles (`CategoryDemoGrid`) so category
pages don't feel empty while the real catalog is small.

- No price, offer count, source count, condition, or freshness fields —
  those read as real commerce facts and must only ever come from real
  Listing/PriceHistory rows.
- Never wire these into compare, save, alerts, or ranking logic.
- Real comparison pages must use stored listings, approved source data, and
  PriceHistory records — this file has no bearing on any of that.
- Demo tiles link to `/search?category=<slug>` (browse the real category),
  never to a fake product detail page.
- Demo tiles reuse each category's existing hero image
  (`public/images/categories/<slug>.png`) rather than fabricating dozens of
  distinct product photos.
